casebody.data:
Marlon L. WATFORD, petitioner,
v.
Natasha DOE, et al. No. 18-6195. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 3, 2018.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals of the Seventh Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
